                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, R</hi> 13). I produce another certifi<lb></lb>cate of the prisoner's conviction—(<hi rend="italic">read—Convicted here Jan.</hi> 1849, <hi rend="italic">having been before convicted; confined eight months</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
